findings.title: checkMaxWallet() function requires sender address to be excluded from the fee
findings.description: The checkMaxWallet() function does not exclude the sender's address from the fee when checking max wallet restriction.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to exclude from fees, change fees, and modify _maxBuyTxAmount and _maxWalletToken when the owner is not renounced.
